          <div class="panel-heading" style="text-align:center;">
            <h4>
              <a> C. Other Awards </a>
            </h4>
          </div>
          <div class="panel-body">
            <ul>
              <li>Directors Medal of Excellence - exclusive award given to students who showed excellence in different fields.</li>
              <li>Character Award - is given to elementary pupils and high school students for Most Obedient, Most Trustworthy
                and Most Responsible.</li>
              <li>Loyalty Gold Medals - are given to all high school graduates who have continuously residency in the school
                from Nursery/Kindergarten/Grade 1 to Fourth Year.</li>
              <li>Other awards may be given depending upon the discretion of school officials to recognize participation and
                performance in school clubs and athletic events, civic action and community service and all inter-school
                activities sanctioned by the school.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
